## Theming / globals.css

O ShadCN canary gera CSS variables em `:root` e `.dark`. Precisamos integrar com o sistema existente:

```css
@import "tailwindcss";
@plugin "tailwindcss-animate"; /* instalado pelo ShadCN */

@custom-variant dark (&:where(.dark, .dark *));

:root {
  /* ShadCN light mode variables */
  --background: oklch(0.98 0 0);       /* ~gray-50 */
  --foreground: oklch(0.145 0 0);      /* ~gray-900 */
  --card: oklch(1 0 0);                /* white */
  --card-foreground: oklch(0.145 0 0);
  --popover: oklch(1 0 0);
  --popover-foreground: oklch(0.145 0 0);
  --primary: oklch(0.546 0.245 264);   /* indigo-500 */
  --primary-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --secondary: oklch(0.961 0 0);       /* gray-100 */
  --secondary-foreground: oklch(0.205 0 0);
  --muted: oklch(0.961 0 0);
  --muted-foreground: oklch(0.556 0 0);
  --accent: oklch(0.961 0 0);
  --accent-foreground: oklch(0.205 0 0);
  --destructive: oklch(0.577 0.245 27); /* red-500 */
  --destructive-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --border: oklch(0.922 0 0);           /* gray-200 */
  --input: oklch(0.922 0 0);
  --ring: oklch(0.546 0.245 264);       /* indigo-500 */
  --radius: 0.5rem;
}

.dark {
  --background: oklch(0.065 0 0);      /* ~gray-950 */
  --foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);      /* ~gray-100 */
  --card: oklch(0.145 0 0);            /* ~gray-900 */
  --card-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --popover: oklch(0.145 0 0);
  --popover-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --primary: oklch(0.546 0.245 264);   /* indigo-500 */
  --primary-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --secondary: oklch(0.205 0 0);       /* gray-800 */
  --secondary-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --muted: oklch(0.205 0 0);
  --muted-foreground: oklch(0.556 0 0);
  --accent: oklch(0.205 0 0);
  --accent-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --destructive: oklch(0.577 0.245 27);
  --destructive-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0);
  --border: oklch(0.205 0 0);           /* gray-800 */
  --input: oklch(0.205 0 0);
  --ring: oklch(0.546 0.245 264);
}
```

